results.title: Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.
results.short_title: Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.
results.latest_major_action: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.
results.summary: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects specified Members to the following House Committees: (1) Agriculture; (2) Education and the Workforce; (3) Foreign Affairs; (4) Homeland Security; (5) the Judiciary; (6) Natural Resources; (7) Oversight and Government Reform; (8) Science, Space, and Technology; (9) Small Business; (10) Transportation and Infrastructure; and (11) Veterans’ Affairs.
